  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2018-08-24",
    "date": "2019-09-03T20:47:24Z",
    "text": "Veterans Valuing Our Widows and Widowers Act or the Veterans VOW Act\n\nThis bill requires the payment of a Medal of Honor special pension to the surviving spouse of a deceased Medal of Honor recipient if that person was married to the recipient for (1) at least one year prior to the veteran's death; or (2) any period of time if a child was born of the marriage or was born to them before the marriage.\n\nThe bill increases the special pension for a living Medal of Honor recipient to $1329.58 per month."
  },
